links.displaytext: As you are observing the ride along you notice the A+D lead looking frustrated and you decide to check in.
Oh no. Why can’t people just read the signs?
Not really. This person hasn’t moved their car yet and they’re in the way of the station install.
Oh jeez. What are we supposed to do then?
We’ll have to call a tow truck and wait for it to move the vehicle. There is a reason why we put these signs up two days before, but sometimes you just can’t get people to follow instructions!
